items.title: Awesome Dos
items.content_text:
### Memory managers

*   [386MAX (⭐130)](https://github.com/sudleyplace/386MAX) - Memory manager for DOS PCs with 386 or higher CPUs, [released by Qualitas company in 1992](https://winworldpc.com/product/386max/6x). Source code was released in June 2022 on GitHub with GPL-3.0 license.

### Open source DOS libraries / Sound Blaster/OPL3

*   [DIGPAK sound drivers source code (⭐35)](https://github.com/jratcliff63367/digpak) - Original source code for the DIGPAK sound drivers uploaded to GitHub by John W. Ratcliff.

items.title: Awesome Agi Cocosci
items.content_text:
### Explainability / Explainable Deep Learning

*   [Noise or Signal: The Role of Backgrounds in Image Classification](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2006.09994.pdf) - ***ICLR'21***, 2021. \[[All Versions](https://scholar.google.com/scholar?cluster=14729938011425134088\&hl=en\&as_sdt=0,5)]. \[[Code & Data (⭐141)](https://github.com/MadryLab/backgrounds_challenge)]. \[[Project](https://gradientscience.org/background/)]. A perspective on image background provides strong clue for foreground classification.
